sentences: Robert Lee "Pops" Popwell (December 29, 1950 – November 27, 2017) was an American jazz-funk bass guitarist and percussionist.
The Young Rascals were inducted into the Rock and Roll Hall of Fame May 6, 1997.
They were inducted into the Vocal Group Hall of Fame in 2005.
Popwell appeared in the movie Hard to Hold with Rick Springfield.
Featured in the 1982 Olivia Newton-John, Live concert video.
